      "outcome": "The Night Courier Depot's routing clerks, caught between the Wardens' collapsing legitimacy and the Families' rising commercial power, agree to a provisional integration trial. The Families' cryptographers begin synchronizing the Depot's routing ledger with the Prayer-Signal Array's transmission schedules. Lacquer artificers seal the first batch of integrated route manifests with the \"doubly authenticated\" stamp. The trial is limited to message-courier traffic only — bulk cargo routing remains under the clerks' independent control — but the Families now have operational access to the ledger's core routing tables. Several senior clerks quietly accept consulting positions within the Signal-House network, enticed by the Families' financial leverage. The Wardens, still fortifying Tower Bridge Concourse, learn of the arrangement too late to intervene. The Families have planted their flag in the Depot — exclusive control is not yet achieved, but the foundation is laid.",
